From your command line, run:

docker build --platform linux/x86_64 -f Dockerfile_base --progress=plain -t minifyer_base .
docker build --platform linux/x86_64 -f Dockerfile --progress=plain -t minifyer:latest .

Then, to push on heroku:

heroku container:login
heroku create minifyer-0-0-0-9000
heroku container:push web --app minifyer-0-0-0-9000
heroku container:release web --app minifyer-0-0-0-9000
heroku open --app minifyer-0-0-0-9000

> Be sure to have the heroku CLI installed.
> You can replace minifyer-0-0-0-9000 with another app name.
